1. *Osim* njega, niko nije rekao ništa. (Except for him, nobody said anything.)
2. Ona nije učestvovala u razgovoru, *osim* da se smeje. (She didn't participate in the conversation, except for laughing.)
3. Svi su trebali da dođu, *osim* njega. (Everyone was supposed to come, except for him.)
4. On je dobio sve, *osim* pravde. (He got everything, except for justice.)
5. *Osim* toga, nisu postojale druge opcije. (Except for that, there weren't any other options.)